The dashboard looks like "unprofessional garbage" because:
1. Widget header is a heavy dark bar (too much chrome)
2. Cards stacked in single column instead of flowing grid
3. Zero content CSS = giant SVG triangles, concatenated text ("Workspaceecho", "Ready 0In Progress 0Blocked 0Done 2")
4. No visual hierarchy, color coding, or proper spacing

## File: `frontend/src/styles.css` — Replace dashboard section (~line 7803 to end of file)

### Design Direction
- **Light chrome**: Thin separator lines instead of heavy dark headers
- **Proper grid flow**: Cards should flow in a responsive masonry-like layout
- **Color-coded content**: Success green, warning amber, danger red, accent blue
- **Typography hierarchy**: Large numbers for stats, small labels for context
- **Consistent spacing**: Use existing design tokens (--space-*, --text-*)

### Shell Redesign (replace .widget-card-header and related)

```css
/* -- Widget card shell — light chrome redesign -- */
.dashboard-widget-card,
.widget-card {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--space-lg);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow 120ms ease, border-color 120ms ease;
}

.dashboard-widget-card:hover,
.widget-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text) 8%, transparent);
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 20%, var(--color-border));
}

/* Light header — thin separator instead of heavy dark bar */
.widget-card-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: var(--space-md-lg) var(--space-xl);
  border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-border) 60%, transparent);
  background: transparent; /* removed heavy dark bg */
}

.widget-card-title {
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin: 0;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

/* Body — remove redundant padding (card has none, body handles it) */
.widget-card-body {
  padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
  flex: 1 1 auto;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.55;
}

/* Edit mode */
.dashboard-widget-grid.is-edit-mode .dashboard-widget-card,
.dashboard-widget-grid.is-edit-mode .widget-card {
  border-style: dashed;
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 40%, var(--color-border));
}
```

### SVG Icon Sizing (critical fix — prevents giant triangles)

